Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry for all the trouble\NI caused the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, don't sweat it.\NThere was a lot of alcohol involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Liquid courage, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a cheater?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I haven't gotten paid at work yet,\Nso this is from my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,humiliatingly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's freeloading!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Off her mother, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's fine! It was cheap anyway,\Nand old and worn out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If this isn't enough,\Ncould I ask you to wait until payday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Extortion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm totally fine with it, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you caught me in\Nsuch a compromising position...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A compromising position?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Phrasing, {\i1}please{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With everything that happened,\Nthis truly is the only thing I can do, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All you did was get my futon a little dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bound to happen--it was your first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your money. Now forget everything!\NLike it never happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A soiled futon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Her first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it never happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Men are scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}my {\i0}phrasing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like things have\Nsettled down for now, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's take a little break, daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hah!\N--There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, Sakurai--how\Ndid Hana's birthday turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't give you much in the way of advice,\Nbut I hope she was happy, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Looks like we touched a nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to go drinking with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So she dragged me to a pub and... we drank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she... no,\Nwe both drank a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, we had missed the last train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was because we were both tipsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Long story short, she wound up\Nspending the night at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me. She {\i1}is {\i0}a woman, for all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my place to say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A grown man, crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth did she {\i1}do{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I had fun at the beach\Nwith the whole gang,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's something about\Nbeing alone on a swaying ship--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Suddenly I'm sensing\Nsomething about to happen in my absence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I shouldn't have come alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Hana's been out of sorts\Never since her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I've told her time\Nand time again not to sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm. She must think\Nshe's done something unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. That'd be way out of character for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Hana makes sure\Nthat line doesn't get crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai, you've never had\Na {\i1}truly {\i0}bad time of it, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a turn-off, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! Nuh-uh! No can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo! Got your phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...\NI didn't... {\i1}not {\i0}not... I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem conflicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So Hana's expressions\Nof love were really razor-thin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's done pondering!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Uzaki's being quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but something's... not right.\NShe's hard to talk to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been through plenty herself--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,she could put on a happy face\Nlike she always has before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Sakurai. Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the fireworks festival nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighborhood association\Ngave us that voucher to use at the stalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You {\i0}are going to invite Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to patch things up, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, it's not like we're arguing or--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though direct involvement\Ngoes against my principles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look: you are {\i1}going{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you say, "Your smile is\Nlike a chrysanthemum firework,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,or "You're beautiful from every angle,\Ntoo, just like those fireworks"--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,compliment the living daylights out\Nof her with that nauseating stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and her mood {\i1}will {\i0}improve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's easy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait--I'm supposed to say {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It touches a father's heart, seeing his daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,speak of men and women\Ndespite her utter lack of experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll give you an excuse to ask her to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure she'd go for it\Nright now if you offered to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Uzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait. There's just so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's fine. I just got here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai... thank you very much\Nfor inviting me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. This thing just will not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm hungry. Want to hit the stalls\Nbefore the show begins?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was delicious. Thank you, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I had that voucher, remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to thank the café owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Still no dice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At a glance, we're {\i1}acting {\i0}all cheery,\Nbut that awkwardness is still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were her usual self...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go goldfish-dipping, Senpai!\NGoldfish-dipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get my loner senpai a roommate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When I picture you telling\Na goldfish "I'm home"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That is {\i1}hilarious{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no. I have to do\Nsomething to lift her spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But {\i1}what{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Compliment the living daylights out\Nof her with that nauseating stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and her mood {\i1}will {\i0}improve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--Uzaki!\N--Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that yukata you're wearing is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom helped me put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice. Really suits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo! That's the ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it looks {\i1}great {\i0}on you, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And those geta sandals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bought them to go with this yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they go {\i1}perfectly{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And your flower hairpin is just so summery!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose that for this yukata, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And your hair--you styled it differently today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So does that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I keep my wallet and my phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you could fit a {\i1}ton {\i0}in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, I {\i1}did {\i0}put\Nin a lot of effort for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And look--I may have managed\Nto charm my dead-inside senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! You're absolutely\Noutstanding today, Uzaki, no lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I? I am, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked really hard, so you better be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd missed this chance,\Nyou would go your entire {\i1}life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and never hang out with a girl in a yukata!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just suck it up. This is miles better\Nthan meek-and-mild Uzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and with you looking so cute and all,\Nwe'd better have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cu"--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cute"?! Do {\i1}you {\i0}really think I'm cute, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes--it just slipped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No... here's my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are {\i0}cute! I'm so glad I invited you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks so much for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful! A knockout!\NYou're cute! {\i1}So {\i0}cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh, you're... you're... you're {\i1}cute{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--That couple's flirting.\N--Cute! Yeah, cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--He sure is desperate.\N--Cute! Yeah, cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,--He's got a weak vocabulary, too.\N--Cute! Yeah, cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Had enough, my darling junior?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too many compliments! I {\i1}get {\i0}it, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, Senpai! Why, you... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Uzaki! Sorry--I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Se...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I swallowed some water...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Practicing by yourself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sakurai-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.\NI thought you'd already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you not\Nto practice alone? It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown me how a few times now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm always watching\Neveryone's practices like a coach--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe by now... I'd be a good swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like I'm not\Nwhere I thought I would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. And after\Neverything you taught me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still a tiny bit frightening.\NEspecially in this dim light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a little more I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll give it my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, why can't I swim better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's really good. No wonder he's a starter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. His movements are so intense,\Nyet he's so quiet--unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm. Relax your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain correct form\Nas you slice through the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine. Human beings generally float.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, right! I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Just... I haven't gotten any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The fireworks festival is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzaki. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}did {\i0}do all that swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're almost there. Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I should apologize, Sakurai-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You went over it with me so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--Gorgeous!\N--So beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Just look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty... and so {\i1}big{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... Uza--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness. You're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I--on Uzaki's lap? Why? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I... pass out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for very long at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The fireworks show hasn't even started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no getting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who helped me carry you\Nsaid that even if you're awake,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you ought to stay lying down for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because my line of sight is\Nblocked... but damn, something smells {\i1}great{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. A thousand times sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, really.\NBesides, this was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I got pretty carried away myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it, truly. I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Man. She'd only just bounced back--and now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I can see it,\Nbut I bet she's making that face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right--the same face\Nshe made back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Ami and the café owner said:\Nshe's thinking about appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But when {\i1}she {\i0}does that?\NIt's only natural things would feel a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When you started at our college last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I didn't think much\Nabout you becoming my junior again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You started getting really\Nbuddy-buddy with me last spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\Nyou seriously got on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:20:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought back on everything\Nthat's happened so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You tagged along everywhere I went,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes even infringing\Non the spaces I used for relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But we hung out together,\Ngoing to the beach and the cat café,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,even reaching the point where\Nthe two of us could go drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And going to see the fireworks,\Nlike we are today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Until last year, I'd never done\Nso much or gone to so many places.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I could do without all the noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but when it comes down to it, it was pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to say it,\Nbut it's probably thanks to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've gotten used to that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, what I'm saying is... don't be so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It messes things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still some summer break left.\NLet's go somewhere again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Well, if you insist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you company on\Nyour loner summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I hope you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure has.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see the fireworks, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just barely?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah--I'm fine right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going tomorrow?\NWherever it is, I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. What {\i1}should {\i0}we do tomorrow, huh?
